{"tha-ap532:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap532:0.2":"Tinadayakavagga ","tha-ap532:0.3":"Sugandhattheraapadana ","tha-ap532:1.1":"“Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","tha-ap532:1.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","tha-ap532:1.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","tha-ap532:1.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","tha-ap532:2.1":"Anubyanjanasampanno, ","tha-ap532:2.2":"battimsavaralakkhano; ","tha-ap532:2.3":"Byamappabhaparivuto, ","tha-ap532:2.4":"ramsijalasamotthato. ","tha-ap532:3.1":"Assaseta yatha cando, ","tha-ap532:3.2":"suriyova pabhankaro; ","tha-ap532:3.3":"Nibbapeta yatha megho, ","tha-ap532:3.4":"sagarova gunakaro. ","tha-ap532:4.1":"Dharaniriva silena, ","tha-ap532:4.2":"himavava samadhina; ","tha-ap532:4.3":"Akaso viya pannaya, ","tha-ap532:4.4":"asango anilo yatha. ","tha-ap532:5.1":"Sa kadaci mahaviro, ","tha-ap532:5.2":"parisasu visarado; ","tha-ap532:5.3":"Saccani sampakaseti, ","tha-ap532:5.4":"uddharanto mahajanam. ","tha-ap532:6.1":"Tada hi baranasiyam, ","tha-ap532:6.2":"setthiputto mahayaso; ","tha-ap532:6.3":"Asaham dhanadhannassa, ","tha-ap532:6.4":"pahutassa bahu tada. ","tha-ap532:7.1":"Janghaviharam vicaram, ","tha-ap532:7.2":"migadayamupeccaham; ","tha-ap532:7.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap532:7.4":"desentam amatam padam. ","tha-ap532:8.1":"Visatthakantavacanam, ","tha-ap532:8.2":"karavikasamassaram; ","tha-ap532:8.3":"Hamsarutehi nigghosam, ","tha-ap532:8.4":"vinnapentam mahajanam. ","tha-ap532:9.1":"Disva devatidevam tam, ","tha-ap532:9.2":"sutvava madhuram giram; ","tha-ap532:9.3":"Pahayanappake bhoge, ","tha-ap532:9.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap532:10.1":"Evam pabbajito caham, ","tha-ap532:10.2":"na cirena bahussuto; ","tha-ap532:10.3":"Ahosim dhammakathiko, ","tha-ap532:10.4":"vicittapatibhanava. ","tha-ap532:11.1":"Mahaparisamajjheham, ","tha-ap532:11.2":"hatthacitto punappunam; ","tha-ap532:11.3":"Vannayim hemavannassa, ","tha-ap532:11.4":"vannam vannavisarado. ","tha-ap532:12.1":"‘Esa khinasavo buddho, ","tha-ap532:12.2":"anigho chinnasamsayo; ","tha-ap532:12.3":"Sabbakammakkhayam patto, ","tha-ap532:12.4":"vimuttopadhisankhaye. ","tha-ap532:13.1":"Esa so bhagava buddho, ","tha-ap532:13.2":"esa siho anuttaro; ","tha-ap532:13.3":"Sadevakassa lokassa, ","tha-ap532:13.4":"brahmacakkappavattako. ","tha-ap532:14.1":"Danto dameta santo ca, ","tha-ap532:14.2":"sameta nibbuto isi; ","tha-ap532:14.3":"Nibbapeta ca assattho, ","tha-ap532:14.4":"assaseta mahajanam. ","tha-ap532:15.1":"Viro suro ca vikkanto, ","tha-ap532:15.2":"panno karuniko vasi; ","tha-ap532:15.3":"Vijitavi ca sa jino, ","tha-ap532:15.4":"appagabbo analayo. ","tha-ap532:16.1":"Anenjo acalo dhima, ","tha-ap532:16.2":"amoho asamo muni; ","tha-ap532:16.3":"Dhorayho usabho nago, ","tha-ap532:16.4":"siho sakko garusupi. ","tha-ap532:17.1":"Virago vimalo brahma, ","tha-ap532:17.2":"vadi suro rananjaho; ","tha-ap532:17.3":"Akhilo ca visallo ca, ","tha-ap532:17.4":"asamo samyato suci. ","tha-ap532:18.1":"Brahmano samano natho, ","tha-ap532:18.2":"bhisakko sallakattako; ","tha-ap532:18.3":"Yodho buddho sutasuto, ","tha-ap532:18.4":"acalo mudito sito. ","tha-ap532:19.1":"Dhata dhata ca santi ca, ","tha-ap532:19.2":"katta neta pakasita; ","tha-ap532:19.3":"Sampahamsita bhetta ca, ","tha-ap532:19.4":"chetta sota pasamsita. ","tha-ap532:20.1":"Akhilo ca visallo ca, ","tha-ap532:20.2":"anigho akathankathi; ","tha-ap532:20.3":"Anejo virajo katta, ","tha-ap532:20.4":"gandha vatta pasamsita. ","tha-ap532:21.1":"Tareta atthakareta, ","tha-ap532:21.2":"kareta sampadarita; ","tha-ap532:21.3":"Papeta sahita kanta, ","tha-ap532:21.4":"hanta atapi tapaso. ","tha-ap532:22.1":"Samacitto samasamo, ","tha-ap532:22.2":"asahayo dayalayo; ","tha-ap532:22.3":"Accherasatto akuho, ","tha-ap532:22.4":"katavi isisattamo. ","tha-ap532:23.1":"Nittinnakankho nimmano, ","tha-ap532:23.2":"appameyyo anupamo; ","tha-ap532:23.3":"Sabbavakyapathatito, ","tha-ap532:23.4":"saccaneyyantagu jino. ","tha-ap532:24.1":"Sattasaravare tasmim, ","tha-ap532:24.2":"Pasado amatavaho; ","tha-ap532:24.3":"Tasma buddhe ca dhamme ca, ","tha-ap532:24.4":"Sanghe saddha mahatthika’. ","tha-ap532:25.1":"Gunehi evamadihi, ","tha-ap532:25.2":"tilokasaranuttamam; ","tha-ap532:25.3":"Vannento parisamajjhe, ","tha-ap532:25.4":"akam dhammakatham aham. ","tha-ap532:26.1":"Tato cutaham tusite, ","tha-ap532:26.2":"anubhotva mahasukham; ","tha-ap532:26.3":"Tato cuto manussesu, ","tha-ap532:26.4":"jato homi sugandhiko. ","tha-ap532:27.1":"Nissaso mukhagandho ca, ","tha-ap532:27.2":"dehagandho tatheva me; ","tha-ap532:27.3":"Sedagandho ca satatam, ","tha-ap532:27.4":"sabbagandhova hoti me. ","tha-ap532:28.1":"Mukhagandho sada mayham, ","tha-ap532:28.2":"padumuppalacampako; ","tha-ap532:28.3":"Parisanto sada vati, ","tha-ap532:28.4":"sariro ca tatheva me. ","tha-ap532:29.1":"Gunatthavassa sabbantam, ","tha-ap532:29.2":"Phalam tu paramabbhutam; ","tha-ap532:29.3":"Ekaggamanasa sabbe, ","tha-ap532:29.4":"Vannayissam sunatha me. ","tha-ap532:30.1":"Gunam buddhassa vatvana, ","tha-ap532:30.2":"hitaya ca na sadisam; ","tha-ap532:30.3":"Sukhito homi sabbattha, ","tha-ap532:30.4":"sangho virasamayuto. ","tha-ap532:31.1":"Yasassi sukhito kanto, ","tha-ap532:31.2":"jutima piyadassano; ","tha-ap532:31.3":"Vatta aparibhuto ca, ","tha-ap532:31.4":"niddoso pannava tatha. ","tha-ap532:32.1":"Khine ayusi nibbanam, ","tha-ap532:32.2":"sulabham buddhabhattino; ","tha-ap532:32.3":"Tesam hetum pavakkhami, ","tha-ap532:32.4":"tam sunatha yathatatham. ","tha-ap532:33.1":"Santam yasam bhagavato, ","tha-ap532:33.2":"vidhina abhivadayam; ","tha-ap532:33.3":"Tattha tatthupapannopi, ","tha-ap532:33.4":"yasassi tena homaham. ","tha-ap532:34.1":"Dukkhassantakaram buddham, ","tha-ap532:34.2":"dhammam santamasankhatam; ","tha-ap532:34.3":"Vannayam sukhado asim, ","tha-ap532:34.4":"sattanam sukhito tato. ","tha-ap532:35.1":"Gunam vadanto buddhassa, ","tha-ap532:35.2":"buddhapitisamayuto; ","tha-ap532:35.3":"Sakantim parakantinca, ","tha-ap532:35.4":"janayim tena kantima. ","tha-ap532:36.1":"Jino te titthikakinne, ","tha-ap532:36.2":"abhibhuyya kutitthiye; ","tha-ap532:36.3":"Gunam vadanto jotesim, ","tha-ap532:36.4":"nayakam jutima tato. ","tha-ap532:37.1":"Piyakari janassapi, ","tha-ap532:37.2":"sambuddhassa gunam vadam; ","tha-ap532:37.3":"Saradova sasankoham, ","tha-ap532:37.4":"tenasim piyadassano. ","tha-ap532:38.1":"Yathasattivasenaham, ","tha-ap532:38.2":"sabbavacahi santhavim; ","tha-ap532:38.3":"Sugatam tena vagiso, ","tha-ap532:38.4":"vicittapatibhanava. ","tha-ap532:39.1":"Ye bala vimatim patta, ","tha-ap532:39.2":"paribhonti mahamunim; ","tha-ap532:39.3":"Niggahim te saddhammena, ","tha-ap532:39.4":"paribhuto na tenaham. ","tha-ap532:40.1":"Buddhavannena sattanam, ","tha-ap532:40.2":"kilese apanesaham; ","tha-ap532:40.3":"Nikkilesamano homi, ","tha-ap532:40.4":"tassa kammassa vahasa. ","tha-ap532:41.1":"Sotunam vuddhimajanim, ","tha-ap532:41.2":"buddhanussatidesako; ","tha-ap532:41.3":"Tenahamasim sappanno, ","tha-ap532:41.4":"nipunatthavipassako. ","tha-ap532:42.1":"Sabbasavaparikkhino, ","tha-ap532:42.2":"tinnasamsarasagaro; ","tha-ap532:42.3":"Sikhiva anupadano, ","tha-ap532:42.4":"papunissami nibbutim. ","tha-ap532:43.1":"Imasmimyeva kappasmim, ","tha-ap532:43.2":"yamaham santhavim jinam; ","tha-ap532:43.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap532:43.4":"buddhavannassidam phalam. ","tha-ap532:44.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap532:44.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap532:44.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap532:45.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap532:45.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap532:45.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap532:46.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap532:46.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap532:46.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap532:47.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sugandho thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap532:48.1":"Sugandhattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap532:49.1":"Tinadayakavaggo tepannasamo. ","tha-ap532:50.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap532:51.1":"Tinado mancado ceva, ","tha-ap532:51.2":"saranabbhanjanappado; ","tha-ap532:51.3":"Supato dandadayi ca, ","tha-ap532:51.4":"nelapuji tatheva ca. ","tha-ap532:52.1":"Bodhisammajjako mando, ","tha-ap532:52.2":"sugandho dasamoti ca; ","tha-ap532:52.3":"Gathasatam satevisam, ","tha-ap532:52.4":"ganitancettha sabbaso. "}